Use Lumo theme tokens (standard Lumo CSS styling tokens) for all styling:
- Prefer Lumo CSS custom properties over custom non-standard styles
- Avoid RGBA backgrounds and custom color values
- Use Lumo's built-in spacing, typography, and color tokens
- Leverage Lumo's adaptive theming capabilities
- Centralize styling through Lumo's design system

This ensures consistent theming and better maintainability across the application.
